{"type": "lens", "id": "prediction-with-missing", "attributes": {"title": "Predicciones con missing features (data skew tipo feature unavailable)", "description": "Distribución de prediction para eventos donde alguna feature llegó faltante en el request. En la demo solo bedrooms se omite (35% del tráfico durante anomalía); el modelo imputa ese hueco con la mediana del training set (bedrooms=3) y predice normal. La predicción es técnicamente válida (HTTP 200) pero estadísticamente débil porque acumula dos fuentes de incertidumbre: la del valor imputado (no es el dato real) y la del modelo en sí. Solo se puebla durante anomalía.", "visualizationType": "lnsXY", "state": {"datasourceStates": {"formBased": {"layers": {"layer1": {"indexPatternId": "model-api-logs", "columns": {"col1": {"label": "prediction", "dataType": "number", "operationType": "range", "sourceField": "prediction", "isBucketed": true, "scale": "interval", "params": {"type": "histogram", "maxBars": 10, "ranges": [{"from": 0, "to": 1000, "label": ""}]}}, "col2": {"label": "Predicciones con missing features", "dataType": "number", "operationType": "count", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ratio", "sourceField": "___records___", "filter": {"language": "kuery", "query": "missing_features: *"}}}, "columnOrder": ["col1", "col2"], "incompleteColumns": {}}}}}, "internalReferences": [], "filters": [], "query": {"language": "kuery", "query": ""}, "visualization": {"legend": {"isVisible": true, "position": "right"}, "valueLabels": "hide", "fittingFunction": "Linear", "axisTitlesVisibilitySettings": {"x": true, "yLeft": true, "yRight": true}, "tickLabelsVisibilitySettings": {"x": true, "yLeft": true, "yRight": true}, "labelsOrientation": {"x": 0, "yLeft": 0, "yRight": 0}, "gridlinesVisibilitySettings": {"x": true, "yLeft": true, "yRight": true}, "preferredSeriesType": "bar", "layers": [{"layerId": "layer1", "accessors": ["col2"], "position": "top", "seriesType": "bar", "showGridlines": false, "layerType": "data", "xAccessor": "col1"}]}}}, "references": [{"type": "index-pattern", "id": "model-api-logs", "name": "indexpattern-datasource-layer-layer1"}]}
{"type": "lens", "id": "top-prediction-outliers", "attributes": {"title": "Top-20 predicciones extremas con feature context", "description": "Las 20 predicciones más altas del rango temporal, con full feature context por evento. La lista está fija ordenada por prediction descendente: si reordenás clickeando otra columna en la UI solo cambiás el orden de visualización, no se re-rankea sobre otra métrica (siguen siendo las top-20 por prediction). Es la entrada al drill-down post-alerta: cuando dispara `PredictionDriftDetected` (Prometheus solo te dice 'el promedio subió'), acá ves los requests específicos que lo causaron y con qué inputs (sqm, bedrooms, neighborhood, latency, model_version, timestamp). Visualiza monitoreo de la cola de la distribución de predicciones (artículo sección 6 'estadísticas básicas: max + distribución completa').", "visualizationType": "lnsDatatable", "state": {"datasourceStates": {"formBased": {"layers": {"layer1": {"indexPatternId": "model-api-logs", "columns": {"col1": {"label": "Request ID", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "string", "operationType": "terms", "sourceField": "request_id", "isBucketed": true, "scale": "ordinal", "params": {"size": 20, "orderBy": {"type": "column", "columnId": "col2"}, "orderDirection": "desc", "otherBucket": false, "missingBucket": false, "parentFormat": {"id": "terms"}}}, "col2": {"label": "Predicción ($)", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "number", "operationType": "max", "sourceField": "prediction", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ratio"}, "col3": {"label": "Square meters", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "number", "operationType": "max", "sourceField": "features.square_meters", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ratio"}, "col4": {"label": "Bedrooms", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "number", "operationType": "max", "sourceField": "features.bedrooms", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ratio"}, "col5": {"label": "Neighborhood", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "string", "operationType": "last_value", "sourceField": "features.neighborhood", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ordinal", "params": {"sortField": "@timestamp"}}, "col6": {"label": "Latencia (ms)", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "number", "operationType": "max", "sourceField": "latency_ms", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ratio"}, "col7": {"label": "Model version", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "string", "operationType": "last_value", "sourceField": "model_version", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ordinal", "params": {"sortField": "@timestamp"}}, "col8": {"label": "Timestamp", "customLabel": true, "dataType": "date", "operationType": "max", "sourceField": "@timestamp", "isBucketed": false, "scale": "ratio"}}, "columnOrder": ["col1", "col2", "col3", "col4", "col5", "col6", "col7", "col8"], "incompleteColumns": {}}}}}, "internalReferences": [], "filters": [], "query": {"language": "kuery", "query": ""}, "visualization": {"layerId": "layer1", "layerType": "data", "columns": [{"columnId": "col1"}, {"columnId": "col2"}, {"columnId": "col3"}, {"columnId": "col4"}, {"columnId": "col5"}, {"columnId": "col6"}, {"columnId": "col7"}, {"columnId": "col8"}], "rowHeight": "single", "rowHeightLines": 1, "headerRowHeight": "single", "headerRowHeightLines": 1, "paging": {"enabled": false, "size": 20}}}}, "references": [{"type": "index-pattern", "id": "model-api-logs", "name": "indexpattern-datasource-layer-layer1"}]}
